  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And a lot of people got sick on the plane.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And like I would say, we arrived in New York.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was a lot of fire station there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They spray foam rubber on the all engine, whole plane.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they told us quicker to get out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I figure, in the plane, that's it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I survived concentration camp, and then I will die in an ocean.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It cannot be.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's impossible.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But somehow, we-- we landed safely in New York.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we came 1950 in New York.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And who were you with on the plane?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the plane were a lot of people-- my wife, my daughter, and myself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was six weeks old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's why we flew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We couldn't go with the ship.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Six weeks old.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very hard for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I came to New York-- we have food from the German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when I come to the United States, it's different thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What we took-- we took a liter-- a liter of food for the baby, for my daughter.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now the food was all right, because we flew for 24 hours. 24 hours it took us to fly from United States to New York.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the last thing, we couldn't get nothing to eat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She have nothing to eat, my daughter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we tell the social worker, we need something to food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My baby crying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what happen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She went to a store, and she brought us a glass of milk.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when baby drink the milk, she throw everything up in a second.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So my wife said, now, this is milk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We cannot do it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they put us took a taxi.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They sent us to Broadway, 100 Broadway, Hotel Hamilton.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And right away, I went in and I cooked it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because we got it-- we got the-- that left-over special thing what we took from Germany.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we cooked it, and we give our daughter to eat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was number one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, we went to Coney Island, to my sister, to my wife's sister.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was supposed to go to New York, from Coney Island, go to New York, go to the doctor.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You should give it a different kind of food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Jewish organization, they-- they put everything together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They tell me, go to this doctor, this address.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Go there.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The doctor will give you the thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Go to the drug store, buy it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I was far away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I memorized where to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Went from Coney Island to Times Square.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Time Square, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Three days, four days.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, for big city-- in your big city, you always memorize.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Went to the doctor, got the prescription.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Went to the drug store, buy the food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Took the-- took the subway all the way to Coney Island, and come home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my wife said, if Nathan doesn't bring the food, we don't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we tried to cook the food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it's different thing with milk, with thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And things we always remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And after this, you know, we came to-- you know, I didn't like to-- I didn't like it to be New York, so my sister-in-law, Regina, said to my wife, please, I have nobody.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I want to be with somebody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Come with your baby.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Come with Sandy-- it's my daughter-- come with you in Detroit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I want you to come to Detroit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my wife said, all right, I'm going to Detroit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said to my wife, no, I want to stay in New York.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But somehow, I said, OK.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I [INAUDIBLE] up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We're going to Detroit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I came here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in two days, I got a job-- ice cream factory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was the mechanic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm supposed to watch that the machine is good, that the oil and everything's working fine, because I was-- I was mechanic-- a plumber.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Plumber is-- he can do almost everything, because we have to do with fire, with water, electricity, you name it, breaking the concrete, fixing the concrete, break the dry wall, fix the dry wall.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So you know, sometimes, repainting the walls, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So that's just like a general contractor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I was really good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I worked there for a year, and I didn't want to work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I said, I want to be a plumber.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I went to a company, and I worked $1 an hour.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Already, I got $1.87 an hour.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I work overtime every day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I brought [INAUDIBLE] $100 a week check home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This week, I brought $40 a week check.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I said to my boss, I cannot work for this money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm working three weeks already, I want a raise.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
